421
00:27:47.635 --> 00:27:49.304
How's Lai?

422
00:27:49.387 --> 00:27:50.305
She plants.

423
00:27:50.388 --> 00:27:51.472
She stomps grapes.

424
00:27:51.556 --> 00:27:52.598
