432
00:28:17.457 --> 00:28:18.874
Something...

433
00:28:20.961 --> 00:28:22.628
More than this?

434
00:28:25.715 --> 00:28:26.674
Yeah.

435
00:28:27.968 --> 00:28:29.635
Ah.

436
00:28:33.223 --> 00:28:34.724
