458
00:29:26.317 --> 00:29:27.402
Trust you?

459
00:29:27.485 --> 00:29:28.528
Trust you?

460
00:29:28.611 --> 00:29:30.815
You are a fucking politician!

461
00:29:34.993 --> 00:29:37.954
